        The project will be located within Egypts New and Renewable Energy Agency (NREA)s 37.5 km2 Benban 1.8 GW PV solar park comprising 39 separate PV plots, situated 12 km east of the nearest village (Benban), and 15 km west of the Nile River. It is close to the Luxor-Aswan road, 40 km northwest of Aswan city, in the Aswan Governorate of Upper Egypt. The project capacity is approximately 64.03 MWp (DC) for a 50 MW inverter nominal power (AC) and occupies a 0.98 km2 plot (SBN 29-4) in the Benban PV solar park 
